            <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-500/10 to-slate-800/50 border border-amber-500/30 rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <span class="text-2xl">рҹ‘‘</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Claude Opus 4.5</h4>
                  <p class="text-amber-400 text-xs">Premium</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Anthropics bГӨsta modell. Djupast mГ¶jliga analys fГ¶r kritiska beslut.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <span class="text-2xl">рҹ”§</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Claude Sonnet</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Standard</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Balanserad - perfekt fГ¶r kod och tekniska frГҘgor.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <span class="text-2xl">рҹ§Ә</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">GPT-5.2</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Resonering</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Step-by-step logik fГ¶r komplexa vetenskapliga frГҘgor.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-emerald-500/10 to-slate-800/50 border border-emerald-500/30 rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <span class="text-2xl">рҹ’Һ</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">GPT-5.2 Pro</h4>
                  <p class="text-emerald-400 text-xs">Premium</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">OpenAIs kraftfullaste modell.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <span class="text-2xl">вҡЎ</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">GPT-4o</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Snabb</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">HГ¶g kvalitet, snabb respons. Bra fГ¶r iteration.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <span class="text-2xl">рҹ“ҡ</span>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Gemini 2.0 Flash</h4>
